<subSubSection pageId="112" pageNumber="109" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="112.[151,1127,219,435]" pageId="112" pageNumber="109">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,280,316,340]" pageId="112" pageNumber="109">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is dedicated to Saneyuki Akiyama (1868–1918), a hero of a popular novel 
<emphasis box="[217,441,349,372]" italics="true" pageId="112" pageNumber="109">Saka-no-ue-no-kumo</emphasis>
whose story is situated in the Matsuyama City, the 
<typeStatus box="[994,1040,348,372]" pageId="112" pageNumber="109">type</typeStatus>
locality of 
<taxonomicName authority="Hoshina, 2012" authorityName="Hoshina" authorityYear="2012" box="[180,306,381,404]" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Leiodes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="112" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="akiyamai" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[180,306,381,404]" italics="true" pageId="112" pageNumber="109">L. akiyamai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[313,395,380,403]" pageId="112" pageNumber="109" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
